originalText.text:
Writing a little thank you to the team at Two Sutton Place North as my review as I am relocating to a different city.

I didn't see any review about this building when I was deciding to move in because it is a new building, but my worries were cleared away immediately on my move-in day. Every staff member at my building went above and beyond to make the entire experience as welcoming and pleasant as possible.

The entire living experience has been so pleasant that if I were to start a family in NYC, I wouldn't hesitate to create my nest here.

The building has everything - the views, the square footage, the fitness facilities, the amazing people (shout out to Eli, Henry, George and Dom for making my stay wonderful), and the proximity to: the greenway along the river, the best Trader Joes in NYC, and easy commute to my work.

It's easily my favorite building in the city. Thank you for having me üôè
